# Oliva Fee__c Flowchart
 
```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Quote or Bind Journey<br/>Oliva context] --> B[OmniScript inserts Fee__c<br/>NB or MTA]
    B --> C[TA_Fee_ConvertFeeAmount<br/>beforeInsert or beforeUpdate]
    C --> D[Fee_Amount__c recalculated<br/>from Quote_Fee_Amount__c + currency rates]
 
    D --> E{Next business event}
 
    E -->|Quote clone or renewal clone| F[CloneQuoteRelatedChildRecords.cloneFeeRecords]
    F --> G[Clone Fee__c rows<br/>set Quote__c = cloned quote]
 
    E -->|Standard cancellation| H[CancelPolicy_NewVersion OS<br/>calls CloneFeeRecords.processFeeRecords]
    H --> I{Option}
    I -->|Fetch| J[Check prior fee rows exist<br/>set REM_PolicyId]
    I -->|Clone| K[Clone prior Fee__c rows<br/>negate amounts<br/>Transaction_Type__c = Cancellation<br/>Category__c = Return]
 
    E -->|Cancel and Reissue| L[CreateTransactionLineItem.UpdateTaxJur<br/>Scenario = CancelAndReissuePolicy]
    L --> M[Clone Fee__c by Submission__c<br/>negate Quote_Fee_Amount__c<br/>Transaction_Type__c = Cancellation<br/>Category__c = Return]
 
    G --> N[CalculatePremiumShare.createPremiumShares]
    K --> N
    M --> N
 
    N --> O[FeeShareProcessor.insertFeeShares]
    O --> P[Create Fee_Share__c rows<br/>cancellation-only selection when present]
 
    P --> Q[Consumption layers<br/>BDX, book of business, policy summary]
 
    classDef oliva fill:#e8f7e8,stroke:#1b5e20,stroke-width:2px,color:#0d3b12;
    classDef shared fill:#fff4e6,stroke:#e07a00,stroke-width:1.5px,color:#6b3d00;
    classDef decision fill:#fff8d6,stroke:#7a5d00,stroke-width:1.5px,color:#3d2f00;
 
    class A,B,F,G,H,I,J,K oliva;
    class C,D,L,M,N,O,P,Q shared;
    class E decision;
 
    linkStyle 0,4,5,6,7,8,9 stroke:#1b5e20,stroke-width:2px;
    linkStyle 1,2,3,10,11,12,13,14 stroke:#e07a00,stroke-width:2px;
    linkStyle 15,16 stroke:#b42318,stroke-width:2.5px;
```
 
 
